- Archive used: `JMdict.xml.gz`, downloaded 2026-07-17
- SHA-256: 08cfdf99863a0859570db7f7e0c8ab49dce8dea1fd090c3b99464fc12d20c81e

Each entry file records the archive digest it was built from in its
`#+JMDICT_SOURCE_SHA256` header.

Russian reference glosses that appear in `Russian reference` sections
(`ru-ref-*`) are JMdict's own `xml:lang="rus"` glosses, reproduced from the
archive above. They are not taken from any other Russian-language source.

EDRDG asks that users acknowledge the usage and source of the files in
