## Open JTalk audio (generated locally; NOT redistributed)

Generated pronunciation audio is synthesised locally with Open JTalk using the
NIT ATR503 M001 HTS voice. It lives under `assets/`, which is excluded from
this repository via `.gitignore`, so no generated audio is distributed here.

- Engine: Open JTalk — https://open-jtalk.sourceforge.net/ (Modified BSD)
- Voice model: nitech_jp_atr503_m001.htsvoice (CC BY 3.0)

Entries reference audio by `ASSET_PATH` and record the engine, voice model,
generation input, licence, and required credit in their `* Media` blocks. If
you build or redistribute this audio, ship the attribution and licence notice
those blocks record. See `docs/org-format.md` for the generation policy.

